NUMBER 655
REGION 50
FIXED_LIGHT
NAME Cloud tops
CALL 33
ITEM 9 693
*DESCRIPTION_START
Walking on the edge of a fluffy white cloud you see a tiny planet the size of a single copper coin, surrounded by utter blackness. Thousands of feet above the nearest cloud layer, your feet rest upon the misty top of a wispy formation. Below, only a few feet of insubstantial white mist separate you from the open space; a fall from this height would surely be eternal.
*DESCRIPTION_END
OUTDOOR_FLOOR
ASTRAL
EXIT NW 656
EXIT N 657
EXIT NE 658
CHANNEL 92
MONSTER_GROUP 57
IFVERB JUMP -1
	ECHO OTHERS %N leaps off the cloud and disappears into the whiteness below.
	ECHO PLAYER You jump off the cloud into the whiteness below.
	MOVE 2083
	AFFECT 2083
	ECHO OTHERS %n appears, falling out of nowhere and slamming onto the rainbow gate.
	DAMAGEPLR CRUSH 40 You slam into the rainbow gate.
	DAMAGEPLR CRUSH 20 You bounce from the massive impact and slam back down.
	DAMAGEPLR CRUSH 10 You bounce from the impact and slam back down.
	DAMAGEPLR CRUSH 5 You bounce a final time and roll to a stop.
	ECHO PLAYER You notice your silver cord again.
ENDIF
