REGION 50
FIXED_LIGHT
NAME Cloud tops
CALL 33
ITEM 9 693
*DESCRIPTION_START
Several large gaps in the clouds below look distinctly like potholes in an otherwise smooth fluff field. Tiny sparks of white lightning arc the open distance inside each, every spark looking alive as it jumps across. Larger bolts of lightning arc across the blue sky here, followed by rolls of thunder that shake the very air.
