NUMBER 692
REGION 50
FIXED_LIGHT
NAME Cloud tops, lightning field
CALL 33
ITEM 9 693
*DESCRIPTION_START
The grey field of cloud comes to an abrupt halt as a steep mountain of white, solid fluff stretches out of the cloud surface and forms a barrier, halting northerly travel. Lightening arcs here and there around you, its accompanying thunder rumbles the 'ground' so that you fear losing your balance occaisionally.
*DESCRIPTION_END
EXIT S 653
EXIT SE 690
EXIT SW 691
ASTRAL
MONSTER_GROUP 68
CHANNEL 92
RANDOM DUMMY1 1 40 0
IFVAR DUMMY1 = 2
	PLREVENT 1
	CONTPLREVENT
        DAMAGEPLR ELECTRIC 20 You are hit by lightning!
        ECHO OTHERS %N is hit by lightning!
	IFVAR FLAG1 = 0
		ECHO PLAYER The cloud rumbles violenty and you are knocked down.
		ECHO OTHERS %N is knocked down as the cloud rumbles.
		POSITION LAY
	ENDIF
ENDIF
IFVAR DUMMY1 = 3
	PLREVENT 1
	CONTPLREVENT
	IFVAR FLAG1 = 0
		ECHO PLAYER The cloud rumbles violenty and you are knocked down.
		ECHO OTHERS %N is knocked down as the cloud rumbles.
		POSITION LAY
	ENDIF
ENDIF
IFVERB SIT -1
	EQUAL FLAG1 1
ENDIF
IFVERB STAND -1
	EQUAL FLAG1 1
ENDIF
